item.title: Wokao
item.description: 111111 final override def map[B, That](f: A => B)(implicit bf: CanBuildFrom[List[A], B, That]): That = { if (bf eq List.ReusableCBF) { if (this eq Nil) Nil.asInstanceOf[That] else { val h = new ::[B](f(head), Nil) var t: ::[B] = h var rest = tail while (rest ne Nil) { val nx = new ::(f(rest.head), Nil) t.tl = nx t = nx rest = rest.tail } h.asInstanceOf[That] } } else super.map(f) } 测试一下
